# Vault-Tec Cybernetic Augments — Locale

# --- Retractable Blades ---
augment-retractable-blades-name = Vault-Tec Retractable Blades Implant
augment-retractable-blades-desc = A Vault-Tec cybernetic implant that conceals retractable blades beneath the forearm skin. Toggle to deploy or retract.
augment-retractable-blades-implanter-name = Vault-Tec Retractable Blades Implanter
augment-retractable-blades-implanter-desc = A single-use surgical syringe loaded with Vault-Tec retractable arm blades.
augment-retractable-blades-action-name = Deploy Blades
augment-retractable-blades-action-desc = Extend or retract the concealed arm blades.
augment-retractable-blades-deploy = Blades extend from your forearm with a sharp click.
augment-retractable-blades-retract = The blades slide back beneath your skin.
augment-retractable-blades-no-hand = You need a free hand to deploy the blades.
augment-retractable-blade-weapon-name = retractable blade
augment-retractable-blade-weapon-desc = A razor-sharp blade extended from a cybernetic arm implant.

# --- Reflex Booster ---
augment-reflex-booster-name = Vault-Tec Reflex Booster Implant
augment-reflex-booster-desc = A Vault-Tec neuro-stimulator implant that temporarily enhances reflexes and movement speed. Causes brief disorientation on expiry.
augment-reflex-booster-implanter-name = Vault-Tec Reflex Booster Implanter
augment-reflex-booster-implanter-desc = A single-use surgical syringe loaded with a Vault-Tec reflex booster implant.
augment-reflex-booster-action-name = Activate Reflex Booster
augment-reflex-booster-action-desc = Floods your nervous system with stimulants, temporarily boosting movement speed. You will crash afterwards.
augment-reflex-booster-activate = Your nerves light up — everything feels faster.
augment-reflex-booster-crash = The stimulant wears off. Your legs buckle as the crash hits.

# --- Targeting HUD ---
augment-targeting-hud-name = Vault-Tec Targeting HUD Implant
augment-targeting-hud-desc = A Vault-Tec optical cybernetic that overlays targeting data on your vision, reducing weapon spread. Passive — always active while installed.
augment-targeting-hud-implanter-name = Vault-Tec Targeting HUD Implanter
augment-targeting-hud-implanter-desc = A single-use surgical syringe loaded with a Vault-Tec targeting HUD implant.
augment-targeting-hud-online = A targeting reticle flickers to life across your vision.

# --- Combat Stim Injector ---
augment-combat-stim-name = Vault-Tec Combat Stim Injector Implant
augment-combat-stim-desc = A Vault-Tec subdermal auto-injector that floods your body with combat stimulants. Boosts melee damage and damage resistance, but poisons you when it wears off.
augment-combat-stim-implanter-name = Vault-Tec Combat Stim Implanter
augment-combat-stim-implanter-desc = A single-use surgical syringe loaded with a Vault-Tec combat stim injector implant.
augment-combat-stim-action-name = Activate Combat Stim
augment-combat-stim-action-desc = Inject combat stimulants for temporary damage boost and resistance. You will suffer toxin damage when it wears off.
augment-combat-stim-activate = Stimulants flood your system — pain fades and your strikes feel heavier.
augment-combat-stim-crash = The combat stim wears off. Toxins burn through your veins.
